    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/50 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">
        Why Choose Our Garden City Location?
      </h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-accent-300 text-2xl font-bold">•</span>
          <span><strong>Central Location:</strong> Easy access from all North Winnipeg neighborhoods</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-accent-300 text-2xl font-bold">•</span>
          <span><strong>Large Team:</strong> 9 experienced dentists to serve you</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-accent-300 text-2xl font-bold">•</span>
          <span><strong>Extended Hours:</strong> Early morning and evening appointments</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-accent-300 text-2xl font-bold">•</span>
          <span><strong>Advanced Technology:</strong> CEREC and SureSmile available</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-accent-300 text-2xl font-bold">•</span>
