  <!-- Map Slot -->
  <div slot="map">
    <GoogleMap 
      locationName="Garden City" 
      address="211-2305 McPhillips Street, Winnipeg, MB R2V 3E1" 
    />
  </div>
  
  <!-- Parking Info -->
  <div slot="parking">
    Free parking is available in our dedicated lot with entrances from both McPhillips Street 
    and the back lane. We have ample parking spaces including designated handicap accessible 
    spots near the main entrance. Evening parking is never an issue with our large lot.
  </div>
  
  <!-- Transit Info -->
  <div slot="transit">
    Conveniently served by multiple Winnipeg Transit routes including the 11, 15, and 77. 
    The nearest bus stop is directly in front of our building on McPhillips Street. 
    We're also just a 10-minute walk from Garden City Shopping Centre transit terminal.
